Audit log information specific to Cloud IAM. This message is
serialized as an ``Any`` type in the ``ServiceData`` message of an
``AuditLog`` message.

Attributes:
    policy_delta (google.iam.v1.policy_pb2.PolicyDelta):
        Policy delta between the original policy and
        the newly set policy.

policy_delta.description: Policy delta between the original policy and the newly set policy.
